Package: scimapClient
Type: Package
Title: Collects and Reports Usage Data on R Packages
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2014-12-16
Author: Christopher Bogart
Maintainer: Christopher Bogart <cbogartdenver@gmail.com>
Description: When this package is loaded, ending your session sends a packet to
    scisoft-net-map.isri.cmu.edu stating an anonymous ID uniquely identifying
    your installation, listing which R packages you had loaded, and how they
    are related. By adding this package to your scripts, or your startup
    profile, you can help the creators/maintainers of scientific software
    packages show the breadth of use and impact of their software to their
    employers, funding agencies, tenure committees, etc.
URL: http://scisoft-net-map.isri.cmu.edu
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
Imports:
    RJSONIO,
    tools,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat
